      <content><![CDATA[<p>An element group is a content element, which references a group of other content elements. Find out, how to use it.</p>
<div class="alert alert-info">Element groups do not work with nested containers. You may prefer <a href="%(link0)">reuse model groups</a> instead.</div>
<div class="alert alert-info alert-danger">Element groups are deprecated and may be removed in upcoming OpenCms versions. At the moment they are still present, but to see them in the "Add wizard", configure them in a module or sitemap configuration.</div>]]></content>
